title: Real Estate Outlook For the Bay Area
description: Compass chief market analyst Patrick Carlisle, along with area agents Dana Green and Val Steele, join Mansion Global reporter Leslie Hendrickson for a talk on the state of the market in the Bay Area, which has seen tremendous growth over the past few decades.
